snippet.title: March of Shrooms - Official Teaser Trailer | Publisher Spotlight Showcase 2023 (Freedom Games)
snippet.description: Take a peek at March of Shrooms in this teaser trailer for the upcoming action RTS, coming to PC. In March of Shrooms, embody a tiny shroom and try to unite all of shroomkind before a massive storm sends everyone back to the mycelial age. Lead a crowd of cheery mushrooms and brawl through the islands. Bring peace, berries, and the peace of mycelium to every agaricus bisporus in the land.
